tauri-plugin-frak-firebase
Copyright 2026 Frak Labs

This plugin is a vendored fork of `tauri-plugin-fcm` (commit `b9d4d186`),
originally authored by Rodolphe Stoclin and the tauri-plugin-fcm contributors.
The upstream project is available at https://github.com/srod/tauri-plugin-fcm
and is dual-licensed under MIT OR Apache-2.0.

The Crashlytics surface was merged in from the previous in-tree
`tauri-plugin-frak-crashlytics` plugin (which itself was Frak Labs original
work under GPLv3) and re-licensed dual MIT OR Apache-2.0 to align with the
upstream FCM plugin license.

Files vendored from `srod/tauri-plugin-fcm` verbatim (or with minimal renames):
- ios/Sources/AppDelegateSwizzler.swift
- ios/Sources/TokenBuffer.swift
- android/src/main/java/com/plugin/frak_firebase/FrakFirebaseMessagingService.kt
  (renamed from FcmMessagingService.kt)
- android/consumer-rules.pro
- src/error.rs
- src/commands.rs (delegate pattern)
- src/mobile.rs (wrapper struct pattern)
- Portions of src/models.rs (FCM-side types)
- Portions of ios/Sources/FrakFirebasePlugin.swift (FCM-side commands +
  MessagingDelegate + UNUserNotificationCenterDelegate)
- Portions of android/src/main/java/com/plugin/frak_firebase/FrakFirebasePlugin.kt
  (FCM-side commands + permission handling)

Files originating from the in-tree `tauri-plugin-frak-crashlytics` plugin:
- src/panic_hook.rs
- Crashlytics-side portions of src/models.rs (SetUserIdArgs, SetKeyArgs,
  LogArgs, RecordErrorArgs, SetCollectionEnabledArgs)
- Crashlytics-side portions of ios/Sources/FrakFirebasePlugin.swift
  (setUserId, setKey, log, recordError, setCollectionEnabled, persisted
  Rust panic forwarder)
- Crashlytics-side portions of
  android/src/main/java/com/plugin/frak_firebase/FrakFirebasePlugin.kt
  (same Crashlytics command set + persisted panic forwarder)

